<section class="outdoor-close" aria-label="Outdoor enquiry prompt">
  <div class="outdoor-wrap outdoor-close__panel">
    <div>
      <p class="outdoor-kicker">Not sure where to start?</p>
      <h2>Send the space. We’ll recommend the right starting point.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="outdoor-close__copy">
      <p>Send the setting, rough size, seating needs and any photos you have. We’ll recommend the surface, base and starting product before anything is priced properly.</p>
      <ol class="outdoor-close__steps" aria-label="Outdoor enquiry process">
        <li>Send photos and rough dimensions.</li>
        <li>We recommend timber, Alfresco porcelain or another starting point.</li>
        <li>Then we price the actual size, finish and delivery.</li>
      </ol>
      <a class="outdoor-btn outdoor-btn--primary" href="/pages/contact?topic=outdoor-furniture">Talk through an outdoor project</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

